            },
            "reviewBody": "So simple but be cautious of the turkey roasting recipe you use. I made this gravy from drippings from my son inlaw's turkey he roasted using bacon and olive oil so the gravy had those flavors incorporated. Still all in all was delicious!",
            "datePublished": "2018-12-25T18:20:32.473Z"
